Steps to run the code as follows:-
 1.Save the code
 
 2.Click on the "Run" button, Compiler dialog box will open.
 
 3.Give the Number of employees.
 
 4.For Example: if the number of employees is 4,
 The goodies that are selected for distribution will be shown on the screen.
 the difference between the chossen goodie with highest price and the lowest price will be printed. i.e: 3121.
 
 5.Now click on the Run button to rerun the program for another input and output.
 
 6. Same as 4th step, we can give any number of employees from 1 to 10, corressponding difference between there highest and lowest price will be printed accordingly.
 
